SortByColumns(
    Filter(
        GNB_MENU,
        LV1 = ThisItem.Result,
        제목 <> LV2Order,
        !IsNumeric(제목),
        !IsEmpty(Users) || !IsEmpty(Teams),
        Office365사용자.MyProfile().Mail in Users.Email || Office365사용자.MyProfile().Mail in Teams.Email
    ),
    "LV2Order",
    SortOrder.Ascending
)
